---
import ExternalLink from "../../components/ExternalLink.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Australian Home Collective handles contact-form information, analytics data and services used to protect and operate the website."
>
  <header class="page-intro">
    <div class="narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        This policy explains the kinds of information Australian Home Collective may collect
        and how it may be used.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="content narrow">
    <h2>Information you provide</h2>
    <p>
      If you use the contact form, we may receive your name, email address and the information
      included in your message. We use this to respond, review feedback or assess corrections,
      guide suggestions or relevant website enquiries.
    </p>
    <p>
      Contact-form submissions are processed by{" "}
      <ExternalLink href="https://formspree.io/security/">Formspree</ExternalLink>. Formspree
      processes and stores form data under its own security and privacy practices.
    </p>
    <h2>Spam protection</h2>
    <p>
      The contact form uses Cloudflare Turnstile to identify automated submissions. Turnstile
      may process technical signals such as an IP address, browser information and the page
      where the check appears. Read the{" "}
      <ExternalLink href="https://www.cloudflare.com/en-in/turnstile-privacy-policy/">
        Cloudflare Turnstile privacy policy
      </ExternalLink>.
    </p>
    <h2>Website analytics</h2>
    <p>
      We use Google Analytics 4 to understand how people find and use this website. It may use
      cookies and collect information such as browser and device details, approximate location,
      referring channels, pages visited and interactions with the site. We use these reports to
      improve content, navigation and website performance.
    </p>
    <p>
      Google processes analytics information under its own terms and privacy practices. You can
      read more about{" "}
      <ExternalLink href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites">
        how Google uses information from sites that use its services
      </ExternalLink>.
    </p>
    <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
    <p>
      Australian Home Collective does not currently publish affiliate links. If affiliate links
      are introduced, partners may use tracking links or cookies to attribute referrals. Their
      privacy practices will be governed by their own policies.
    </p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy questions, use the <a href="/contact/">Contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
